Class Preferences

java.lang.Object
  com.fewstera.injectablemedicinesguide.Preferences

public class Preferences
extends java.lang.Object

Preferences class for the application This is class is responsible for interacting with the phones PreferenceManager. This is used to store data locally for the user.
